oses type safety as untagged errors merge together in the Effect failure channel. Consider using a tagged error and optionally wrapping the original in a 'cause' property.    effect(globalErrorInEffectFailure)","category":0,"code":35,"source":"effect"}]],[1618,[{"start":1176,"length":1,"messageText":"'a' is possibly 'undefined'.","category":1,"code":18048},{"start":1198,"length":1,"messageText":"'a' is possibly 'undefined'.","category":1,"code":18048},{"start":1239,"length":1,"messageText":"'a' is possibly 'undefined'.","category":1,"code":18048},{"start":1295,"length":1,"messageText":"'a' is possibly 'undefined'.","category":1,"code":18048},{"start":1316,"length":1,"messageText":"'a' is possibly 'undefined'.","category":1,"code":18048},{"start":1376,"length":10,"messageText":"Object is possibly 'undefined'.","category":1,"code":2532},{"start":1433,"length":1,"messageText":"Type 'undefined' cannot be used as an index type.","category":1,"code":2538},{"start":1475,"length":1,"messageText":"Type 'undefined' cannot be used as an index type.","category":1,"code":2538},{"start":1527,"length":1,"code":2345,"category":1,"messageText":{"messageText":"Argument of type 'string | undefined' is not assignable to parameter of type 'string'.","category":1,"code":2345,"next":[{"messageText":"Type 'undefined' is not assignable to type 'string'.","category":1,"code":2322}]}}]],[3982,[{"start":1588,"length":22,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":{"messageText":"Type '<O>(query: Query<O>) => Effect.Effect<Option.None<O | undefined> | Option.Some<O | undefined>, SqlError, never>' is not assignable to type '<O>(query: Query<O>) => Effect<Option<O>, SqlError, never>'.","category":1,"code":2322,"next":[{"messageText":"Type 'Effect<None<O | undefined> | Some<O | undefined>, SqlError, never>' is not assignable to type 'Effect<Option<O>, SqlError, never>' with 'exactOptionalPropertyTypes: true'. Consider adding 'undefined' to the types of the target's properties.","category":1,"code":2375